WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomElmLookingForYou:
    .string "Mom: Oh, {PLAYER}! Our neighbor, Prof. Elm,\n"
    .string "was looking for you. He said he\l"
    .string "wanted you to do something for him.$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomTohoNavBackFromRepair:
    .string "Mom: Oh! I almost forgot! Your TōhōNav is\n"
    .string "back from the repair shop.\l"
    .string "Here you go!$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomTohoNavReceive:
    .string "Mom: Your TōhōNav is essential,\n"
    .string "if you want to be a good Puppeteer.$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomSetTime:
    .string "Mom: Oh? The time of day isn't set.\n"
    .string "You mustn't forget that!$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomTohoNavQuestion:
    .string "Mom: By the way, do you know how to use\n"
    .string "the map feature in the TōhōNav?$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomTohoNavExplanation:
    .string "Mom: Turn on the TōhōNav and select the\n"
    .string "Map icon. You can see your current\l"
    .string "location and plan your route.\l"
    .string "It's really helpful!$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomTohoNavSummary:
    .string "Mom: Just open the TōhōNav and use the\n"
    .string "Map feature to navigate. \p"
    .string "You'll get the hang of it quickly!$"

WakabaTown_PlayersHouse_1F_Text_MomGeneric:
    .string "Mom: Good luck on your adventure!\n"
    .string "Call if you need anything!$"
